definition: abbr. for Canada 加拿大[Jia1 na2 da4]/surname Jia

to add/plus/(used after an adverb such as 不, 大, 稍 etc, and before a disyllabic verb, to indicate that the action of the verb is applied to sth or sb previously mentioned)/to apply (restrictions etc) to (sb)/to give (support, consideration etc) to (sth)

sentences.english: And the multitude said, This is Jesus the prophet of Nazareth of Galilee.
sentences.chinese: 衆人說，這是加利利拿撒勒的先知耶穌。

sentences.english: Roman soldiers had killed some Galileans who had been offering sacrifices.
sentences.chinese: 羅馬士兵殺害了一些獻祭的加利利人。

sentences.english: This is the difference. The Sea of Galilee receives but does not keep the Jordan.
sentences.chinese: 加利利海接納約旦河水但並不守着河一滴不放。

sentences.english: Then cometh Yeshua from Galilee to Jordan unto John, to be baptized of him.
sentences.chinese: 耶斯華從加利利來到約旦河找約翰，受他的洗。

sentences.english: This parable was told while he was in Galilee.
sentences.chinese: 這是他在加利利時講的。

sentences.english: These men probably knew everything about the Lake of Galilee, more than anybody else.
sentences.chinese: 他們可以說比任何人更熟悉加利利湖的一切情況。

sentences.english: The Sea of Galilee, in Israel, is a freshwater lake.
sentences.chinese: 以色列的加利利海，是淡水湖。
他們在尋找一些加利利人。

sentences.english: A city of ancient Palestine on the northwest shore of the Sea of Galilee.
sentences.chinese: 古巴勒斯坦一城市，位於加利利海的西北海岸。

sentences.english: When the blue wave rolls nightly on deep Galilee.
sentences.chinese: 加利利夜海翻騰藍色波浪。

sentences.english: The city of Caesarea Philippi was about 25 kms north of the Sea of Galilee.
sentences.chinese: 凱撒利亞腓立比城大約在加利利海以北二十五公里處。

sentences.english: Fishing in the Sea of Galilee seemed to have been a very prosperous business.
sentences.chinese: 在加利利湖捕魚在當時似乎是一個蓬勃的行業。

sentences.english: But some said, Shall Christ come out of Galilee?
sentences.chinese: 但也有的說，基督豈是從加利利出來的嗎。

sentences.english: Jesus and the disciples then began to sail across the lake.
sentences.chinese: 耶穌和門徒隨後開始乘船度過加利利湖。

sentences.english: Who says the Messiah is supposed to come from Galilee?
sentences.chinese: 彌賽亞豈是從加利利出來的嗎？

sentences.english: 44And he kept on preaching in the synagogues of Judea.
sentences.chinese: 44於是耶穌在加利利的各會堂傳道。
